                    "message": {
                        "text": "Reentrancy in FinancialPoolManager._selectWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#333-391):\n\tExternal calls:\n\t- (success,None) = address(winner).call{value: pool.goodValue}() (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#376)\n\tState variables written after the call(s):\n\t- pool.winnersCount ++ (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#382)\n\tFinancialPoolManager.pools (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#72) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- FinancialPoolManager._selectWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#333-391)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.activatePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#188-205)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.createPool(string,uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#149-182)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.deletePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#211-219)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getAllParticipants(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#503-510)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getParticipantCount(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#479-481)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getParticipantInfo(uint256,address) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#489-496)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#398-429)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.isParticipant(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#125-131)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.leavePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#250-274)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.notParticipant(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#133-139)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.onlyPoolOwner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#109-115)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.participateInPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#225-244)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#280-327)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.poolStatus(uint256,FinancialPoolManager.PoolStatus) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#117-123)\n\t- pool.status = PoolStatus.Finished (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#388)\n\tFinancialPoolManager.pools (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#72) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- FinancialPoolManager._selectWinner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#333-391)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.activatePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#188-205)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.createPool(string,uint256,uint256,uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#149-182)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.deletePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#211-219)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getAllParticipants(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#503-510)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getParticipantCount(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#479-481)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getParticipantInfo(uint256,address) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#489-496)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.getPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#398-429)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.isParticipant(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#125-131)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.leavePool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#250-274)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.notParticipant(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#133-139)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.onlyPoolOwner(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#109-115)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.participateInPool(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#225-244)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.payInstallment(uint256) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#280-327)\n\t- FinancialPoolManager.poolStatus(uint256,FinancialPoolManager.PoolStatus) (../sb/Consorcio_F.sol#117-123)\n"
